race.comment: Potentially a handy maiden. MARINE EMPRESS (7) resumes having run close up in two runs last time in at Geelong, sent out the $1.65 favourite at her second career start. Expecting she's taken improvement over the spell and should take beating here. WOLFOFFITROYSTREET (6) was sent out favourite on debut at Echuca and hit the line well for third, beaten 1.3 lengths. He should relish the extra 100m from a soft draw and can take this out. COOLY (10) is knocking on the door and should appreciate getting over a bit more ground now. BANXI (3) did enough fresh in a small field at Kyneton on wet ground. Expect improvement off that.
